<section class="reviews-section">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">Amazon Verified Reviews</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Real People. Real Results.</h2>
      <div class="overall-rating">
        <span class="stars-lg">★★★★★</span>
        <span class="rating-summary">4.9 out of 5 on Amazon</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="reviews-grid">

      <div class="review-card">
        <div class="review-card-top">
          <div class="review-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <span class="rv-flavor-tag rv-blue">Blue Raspberry</span>
        </div>
        <div class="review-title">Tastes great</div>
        <blockquote>"Best adaptogen drink I've tried! Love the mild relaxed feeling from the magnesium. Tastes great without being too sweet or having a fake sugar/stevia taste."</blockquote>
        <div class="reviewer">
          <div class="reviewer-avatar" style="background:#3B6FF0;">SB</div>
          <div>
            <strong>Shannon Brown</strong>
            <div class="reviewer-tag">
              <svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#F5A623"><path d="M12 2l2.4 7.4H22l-6.2 4.5 2.4 7.4L12 17l-6.2 4.3 2.4-7.4L2 9.4h7.6z"/></svg>
              Verified Amazon Purchase
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="review-card">
        <div class="review-card-top">
          <div class="review-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <span class="rv-flavor-tag rv-watermelon">Watermelon</span>
        </div>
        <div class="review-title">Great focus/mental drink!</div>
        <blockquote>"This is my favorite flavor — watermelon. Immediately after a few sips, you can feel the effects in your brain. I believe this is the only drink that does this."</blockquote>
        <div class="reviewer">
          <div class="reviewer-avatar" style="background:#E84C6B;">KM</div>
          <div>
            <strong>Kristine Manlapaz</strong>
            <div class="reviewer-tag">
              <svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#F5A623"><path d="M12 2l2.4 7.4H22l-6.2 4.5 2.4 7.4L12 17l-6.2 4.3 2.4-7.4L2 9.4h7.6z"/></svg>
              Verified Amazon Purchase
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="review-card">
        <div class="review-card-top">
          <div class="review-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <span class="rv-flavor-tag rv-mango">Mango</span>
        </div>
        <div class="review-title">Happie Fungi!</div>
        <blockquote>"Refreshing mango flavor with light fizz. Not overly sweet, and I felt a smooth boost in focus without caffeine jitters. Great afternoon alternative to soda."</blockquote>
        <div class="reviewer">
          <div class="reviewer-avatar" style="background:#F5A623;color:#1A1A1A;">NC</div>
          <div>
            <strong>Natalie Cesare</strong>
            <div class="reviewer-tag">
              <svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#F5A623"><path d="M12 2l2.4 7.4H22l-6.2 4.5 2.4 7.4L12 17l-6.2 4.3 2.4-7.4L2 9.4h7.6z"/></svg>
              Verified Amazon Purchase
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="review-card">
        <div class="review-card-top">
          <div class="review-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <span class="rv-flavor-tag rv-watermelon">Watermelon</span>
        </div>
        <div class="review-title">Surprisingly Good Taste and Steady Energy</div>
        <blockquote>"Wasn't sure what to expect, but the watermelon flavor is actually really refreshing. It makes me feel clear, focused, and with smooth energy throughout the day."</blockquote>
        <div class="reviewer">
          <div class="reviewer-avatar" style="background:#E84C6B;">WR</div>
          <div>
            <strong>wendolin reyes</strong>
            <div class="reviewer-tag">
              <svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#F5A623"><path d="M12 2l2.4 7.4H22l-6.2 4.5 2.4 7.4L12 17l-6.2 4.3 2.4-7.4L2 9.4h7.6z"/></svg>
              Verified Amazon Purchase
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="review-card">
        <div class="review-card-top">
          <div class="review-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <span class="rv-flavor-tag rv-mango">Mango</span>
        </div>
        <div class="review-title">Love it — replaced morning coffee</div>
        <blockquote>"My wife and I have replaced morning coffee with this drink and we are loving it. Big fan of mango and blueberry flavors."</blockquote>
        <div class="reviewer">
          <div class="reviewer-avatar" style="background:#F5A623;color:#1A1A1A;">NG</div>
          <div>
            <strong>Nicole G</strong>
            <div class="reviewer-tag">
              <svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#F5A623"><path d="M12 2l2.4 7.4H22l-6.2 4.5 2.4 7.4L12 17l-6.2 4.3 2.4-7.4L2 9.4h7.6z"/></svg>
              Verified Amazon Purchase
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="review-card">
        <div class="review-card-top">
          <div class="review-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <span class="rv-flavor-tag rv-blue">Blue Raspberry</span>
        </div>
        <div class="review-title">Refreshing, Clean Energy Without the Crash!</div>
        <blockquote>"Best adaptogen drink I've tried! Love the mild relaxed feeling. Tastes great without being too sweet — exactly what I look for in a functional beverage."</blockquote>
        <div class="reviewer">
          <div class="reviewer-avatar" style="background:#3B6FF0;">L</div>
          <div>
            <strong>Luciana</strong>
            <div class="reviewer-tag">
              <svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#F5A623"><path d="M12 2l2.4 7.4H22l-6.2 4.5 2.4 7.4L12 17l-6.2 4.3 2.4-7.4L2 9.4h7.6z"/></svg>
              Verified Amazon Purchase
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div style="text-align:center;margin-top:40px;">
      <a href="/pages/reviews" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:transparent;border:2px solid var(--green);color:var(--green);border-radius:50px;padding:13px 32px;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;transition:all 0.2s;">
        Read All Reviews →
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
.review-card-top { display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; margin-bottom:8px; }
.review-title { font-size:13px; font-weight:800; color:#111; margin-bottom:8px; }
.rv-flavor-tag { font-size:10px; font-weight:800; letter-spacing:0.07em; text-transform:uppercase; padding:3px 10px; border-radius:50px; flex-shrink:0; }
.rv-blue { background:rgba(59,111,240,0.1); color:#2855D4; }
.rv-watermelon { background:rgba(232,76,107,0.1); color:#C03060; }
.rv-mango { background:rgba(245,166,35,0.12); color:#B8730A; }
.reviewer-tag { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:4px; font-size:11px; color:#888; margin-top:2px; }
.reviewer-avatar { width:36px; height:36px; border-radius:50%; color:#fff; font-size:12px; font-weight:800; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; flex-shrink:0; background:var(--green-dark); }
</style>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Reviews Section",
  "settings": []
}
{% endschema %}
